       Thoughtful Investing.

     


       At Sigma, thoughtful investing begins by listening. We want to understand where each client is today and where they want to be tomorrow. This allows us to find creative solutions that meet their unique financial objectives.

     







     Our Team.

   


     Our most important asset is our team of professionals.  Sigma’s portfolio managers have an      
     average of over 20 years of investment experience between them.  In addition, the dedicated 
     operations staff is committed to providing a proactive and highly personalized client experience.

   







   Core Values.

 


  At Sigma Investment Counselors, we embrace honesty, integrity, competency, leadership,    
  fairness, accountability, and teamwork as our core values.















View Our Locations
Sigma Investment Counselors is dedicated to serving our clients wherever they might be. Find out more about our multiple office locations.
